Razgulay Slides for First Day in Three as White Sugar Declines

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-08-16T09:35:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-16/razgulay-slides-for-first-day-in-three-as-white-sugar-declines.html
OAO Razgulay, a Russian sugar
producer, dropped for the first day in three as white sugar fell
in  London .  The shares decreased as much as 3.7 percent and last traded
1.3 percent lower at 37.49 rubles by 1:23 p.m. in Moscow.  White sugar fell as much as 1.2 percent to $727.30 a ton on
the NYSE Liffe exchange in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  